# Prompt: Implement Complete Image Tools Suite for phung.work
## Objective
Build a professional, browser-first **Image Tools** module for **phung.work** comparable to TinyWow, iLoveIMG, Squoosh, Canva Utilities and other modern online image tool platforms.
This module should become one of the flagship sections of the website.
The implementation must follow the existing architecture, design system, routing, and reusable components already used by phung.work.
---
# Core Principles
* Everything runs locally in the browser whenever technically possible.
* User images never leave the browser unless explicitly required.
* No backend dependency for standard image processing.
* AI features should use WebAssembly/WebGPU/WebML/ONNX Runtime Web where feasible.
* Fast.
* Mobile responsive.
* Desktop optimized.
* Dark mode.
* Accessible (WCAG AA).
* Modular architecture.
* Lazy loading.
* Code splitting.
* Reusable components.
Do NOT modify existing application architecture unless absolutely necessary.
